collection.name: Toxic Skulls Club
collection.description:
Toxic Skulls Club is a community driven collection of 9,999 unique Toxic Skulls NFTs.

Being a Toxic Skulls Club holder grants you access to holders only benefits such as exclusive drops, events and more. Each Toxic Skull allows its holder to vote on experiences, future perks and utilities that will be paid by the Community Wallet.

Visit www.ToxicSkullsClub.io for more details.

Stay Toxic!
